  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">A certain college had 3,000 students enrolled in 2015. The college predicts that after 2015, the number of students enrolled each year will be 2%&nbsp;less than the number of students enrolled the year before. Which of the following functions models the relationship between the number of students enrolled, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x\"></span>, and the number of years after 2015, <span class=\"italic\">x</span>&nbsp;?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
