      "content": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph \"><span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, 0 point 0 2, times open parenthesis, 3,000, close parenthesis, to the x power\"></span></span></p>\n"
